OL,3,CSeries of failures allowed rapist to
OL,4,Cstrike again and murder college student
OL,6,FFailures by police, probation services
OL,7,Fand the NHS meant a convicted rapist
OL,8,Fwas able to enrol at a college where
OL,9,Fhe befriended then murdered a young
OL,10,Fwoman, an inquest has found.
OL,12,FElizabeth McCann, 26, was raped and
OL,13,Fstrangled by Simon Goold, a fellow
OL,14,Fstudent at the Health and Wellbeing
OL,15,Fcollege in Ashton-under-Lyne, Greater
OL,16,FManchester.
