OL,3,CSeries of failures allowed rapist to
OL,4,Cstrike again and murder college student
OL,6,FGoold, 52, had previously been
OL,7,Fconvicted of rape, sexual assault and
OL,8,Fwounding in 2010 and it was known that
OL,9,Fhe posed a real danger to "lone women"
OL,10,Fin "certain circumstances", especially
OL,11,Fwhen alcohol or when he felt rejected.
OL,13,FBut, he was admitted into the Health
OL,14,Fand Wellbeing College without a risk
OL,15,Fassessment taking place.
OL,17,FSenior Coroner Alison Mutch said this
OL,18,F"probably" contributed to Ms McCann's
OL,19,Fdeath.
