OL,4,Cstrike again and murder college student
OL,6,FProbation and police also failed to
OL,7,Fproperly act on a number of warning
OL,8,Fsigns, including Goold telling them he
OL,9,Fdescribed as a 'small relapse' with
OL,10,Falcohol and an admission that a woman
OL,11,Fhe hoped to become 'intimate' with had
OL,12,Fdecided not to pursue the relationship.
OL,14,FBut police and probation "failed to
OL,15,Fexhibit any professional curiosity",
OL,16,Fprobably due to their "large
OL,17,Fworkloads", said Ms Mutch.
