OL,6,FShe added: "It is possible that this
OL,7,Flack of action by Greater Manchester
OL,8,FPolice (GMP) and probation contributed
OL,9,Fto Elizabeth's death."
OL,11,FThe inquest, in Stockport, also heard
OL,12,Fthe college, which is run by NHS
OL,13,Fmental health trust Pennine Care, and
OL,14,Fprobation had failed to set up an
OL,15,F'effective referral system' to manage
OL,16,F'high risk' students such as Goold.
