OL,6,FAn incident in a Wetherspoons pub in
OL,7,FAshton in July 2022, where an
OL,8,Finebriated Goold tried to kiss Ms
OL,9,FMcCann's friend, a former student
OL,10,Fturned volunteer at the college, was
OL,11,Fnot recognised as 'high risk' by the
OL,12,Fcollege.
OL,14,FThat meant the college's senior
OL,15,Fmanager failed to inform probation
OL,16,Fservices and instead dealt with it
OL,17,F'informally' by speaking with Goold to
OL,18,Ftell him his behaviour was
OL,19,Finappropriate.
