OL,6,FMs Mutch wrote: "As a consequence
OL,7,F(Goold) continued at the college and
OL,8,Fprobation were unaware of these events
OL,9,Fand no action was taken by them.
OL,11,F"It is probable that had there not
OL,12,Fbeen a failure to share the July 2022
OL,13,Fincident which was caused by the
OL,14,Fprevious failures Elizabeth McCann
OL,15,Fwould not have died on the day she
OL,16,Fdid."
