OL,6,FMs Mutch recorded a conclusion of
OL,7,Funlawful killing and in February 2023,
OL,8,FGoold, of Manchester Road in Ashton,
OL,9,Fwas jailed for life and ordered to
OL,10,Fserve a minimum of 35 years at
OL,11,FManchester Crown Court after he
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to murder, rape, sexual
OL,13,Fassault and assault by penetration on
OL,14,Fthe second day of his trial.
OL,16,FThe court heard how Goold deliberately
OL,17,Ftargeted Ms McCann, of Hyde, after
OL,18,Fseeing her at the college.
