OL,6,FOn 25 August, 2022, he met her at a
OL,7,Fpub in Ashton, where he plied her with
OL,8,Fdrinks until he took her back to his
OL,9,Fflat where he raped and strangled her,
OL,10,Fbefore reporting her death to the
OL,11,Fpolice the following day.
OL,13,FIn a victim personal statement read to
OL,14,Fthe court, Ms McCann's mother, Debbie
OL,15,FMcCann, said: "We have seriously
OL,16,Fstruggled to accept that she is gone.
OL,17,FI keep trying to ring her in an
OL,18,Fattempt to speak to her again.
