OL,4,Cstrike again and murder college student
OL,6,F"No parent should have to survive
OL,7,Fwithout their child. As her mother I
OL,8,Ffelt her death was my responsibility
OL,9,Fas I failed to protect her.
OL,11,F"Lizzie's personality touched everyone
OL,12,Fwho met her. She was the most amazing,
OL,13,Fbeautiful daughter, sister and mother
OL,14,Fanyone could ever ask for and we will
OL,15,Falways miss her."
OL,17,FDr Simon Sandhu, medical director at
OL,18,FPennine Care NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,19,Fsaid: "We want to offer our sincere
OL,20,Fcondolences and apologies to
OL,21,FElizabeth's family.
