OL,6,F"We fully accept the conclusion of the
OL,7,Fcoroner who found that significant
OL,8,Ffailings at the college where
OL,9,FElizabeth was enrolled probably
OL,10,Fcontributed to her death.
OL,12,F"We are now commissioning an
OL,13,Findependent review of the college
OL,14,Fwhich will consider all the findings
OL,15,Ffrom the inquest.
OL,17,F"We are committed to the safety of all
OL,18,Four students and we are truly sorry
OL,19,Fthat we failed to have systems and
OL,20,Fprocesses in place that could have
OL,21,Fprotected Elizabeth."
