OL,6,FA Probation Service spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"This was a horrific crime and we have
OL,8,Fapologised to Elizabeth McCann's loved
OL,9,Fones for the failings in this case.
OL,11,F"We have taken steps to address the
OL,12,Fissues identified in the report and
OL,13,Finquest, including improving
OL,14,Finformation sharing and recruiting
OL,15,Fthousands more probation staff across
OL,16,Fthe country.
OL,18,F"In light of the coroner's findings,
OL,19,Fwe will further review our next steps
OL,20,Fto ensure we have taken any action
OL,21,Fneeded to keep the public safe."
