OL,6,FA GMP spokesperson said: "Our thoughts
OL,7,Fand sincere condolences remain with
OL,8,FElizabeth's family. We respect the
OL,9,Ffindings made by the coroner around
OL,10,Fcase handling and offender management.
OL,12,F"A full review has taken place to
OL,13,Fensure that we continue to make
OL,14,Ffurther improvements in these areas,
OL,15,Fwhile also providing the best possible
OL,16,Fcare and protection to those the force
OL,17,Fcomes into contact with."
